. Anyhow mother said, well, take off your shoes. And - go there and have a good wash my lady. So I had a good wash. She said, and up you go. So she had a little dark cupboard in her room, and I was put in this dark cupboard - oh maybe a quarter of an hour
 
or twenty minutes, that was long enough. So then mother said, now you can get out of there and you can go in the bed, there's no tea for you. So I was up in there and father was creeping up - with a bit of something for me to eat. So that was one punishme
nt - that I had. That was severe punishment, that was more severe than any.
